    <item>
      <title>美国限制华为人工智能产品，中国芯片发展受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-s-chip-advances-stall-as-us-curbs-hit-huawei-ai-product</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华为技术有限公司 (Huawei Technologies Co.) 立志为人工智能和智能手机打造更强大的芯片，但因美国的制裁而遭遇重大障碍，阻碍了中国赶超美国技术的重大努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-s-chip-advances-stall-as-us-curbs-hit-huawei-ai-product</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 08:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
